ROS 使用
Setup workspace
1. Create your workspace
    mkdir -p ~/robotics/src  //robotics = name of your workspace
    cd ~/robotics/src
    catkin_init_workspace
    
2. build the workspace
    cd ~/robotics
    catkin_make
    
3. Link workspace with ros
    souce ~/robotics/devel/setup.bash   // or setup.zsh
    
4. create a node in workspace
    cd ~/robotics/src
    catkin_create_pkg first_node rospy std_msgs

5. create our first node in Python
    mkdir ~/robotics/src/first_node/script
    gedit first_node.py

6. building and running the node
    chmod +x first_node.py
    cd ~/robotics
    catkin_make

7. try
    roscore
    rosrun first_node first_node.py

8. sudo apt-get install ros-kinetic-Package    

9.  rosnode 
    rostopic
    rostopic type [topic]
    rostopic echo [topic]


删除ros自带的cv2.so (搜索删除)
删除/opt/ros/kinetic/share/OpenCV-3.3.1-dev
删除/opt/ros/kinetic/lib/aarch64-linux-gnu/libopencv-*
